	(1101, 426, 'en', '<p>In order to create your own community, first you will need to request it to synapseshub. This request is needed in order to avoid two communities with same content in the platform.</p>\r\n<p>Please fill the form below in order to submit your request.</p>'),
	(1102, 426, 'es', '<p>Para crear su propia comunidad, haga una requisici&oacute;n para synapseshub. Eso es neces&aacute;rio para que no existan dos comunidades con mismo contenido en la plataforma.</p>\r\n<p>Para enviar tu solicitud, s&oacute;lo tienes que rellenar el siguiente formulario.</p>'),
